args: Then the rumor of the Syndicate\nperforming a massive experiment...\nIt was a lie?
It doesn't matter. There was a chance,\nso I had to be sure.
All I need is a whiff of Syndicate stink,\nand I'll drop everything to chase it down.
I know, but you gotta pace yourself, okay?\nYour body's not as infallible as you\nlike to believe.
You can save your worries, Andromeda.\nThere's nothing here to get worked\nup over anyway.
Yes... Hm? Hold on! I sense a powerful\nsource of mana approaching us!
Wow, right into my trap. I figured a failure\nlike you would be impatient, but that was\nway too easy.
Name's Bellina.\nI'm here to kill you.
You've caused quite a stir with your rise\nagainst the Syndicate, you know.

Subject Tf-997 of the Synthetic
Shapeshifting Project, a guinea pig for
artificial shapeshifting—one that scurried
off before he could be put down.
And now you've got the guts to seek\nrevenge? You shoulda kept running.
I'm free to do what I want.
That power... You were a Syndicate\nexperiment yourself.
Hey now, don't go lumpin' me in with you.\nI ain't no patchwork failure.

You were merged with a dragon by force,
and the results aren't pretty. But me?
I got pure mana transferred into my arm,
sapped straight from a dragon.
I don't need to shapeshift to tap into my\nfull power. It's just there, always, waiting\nto be unleashed.
Still, failure though you may be, they\nhad to call ME in to kill you. I'm hoping\nthat means you'll put up a fight.
Give it a try. I'll crush any and all that\nstand between me and destroying the\nSyndicate.
I will destroy ALL TRACES of the Syndicate!
Bring it! I'll show you that\nI'm the strongest of all!
Not bad! But I think warm-ups are over.\nTime to bring it for real!
Hmph... I see you really were\nholding back.
And you still are. You won't be able to\ntake me on like that!
Rrgh! It's taking all I have just to guard!
Ha ha ha! You can't beat me if all you do\nis defend!
You'll regret making me use this...\nWYRMBINDING!
Yes, FINALLY! It's been ages since I could\nuse my full power with someone.\nAnd believe me, I'm gonna savor it.
Rrrgh... Enough! Feel the savage wrath\nof the dragon within me!
I'm the strongest!\nYOU'RE just a failure!\nYou—
You call me a failure, and yet you\ncan't even control your own power?\nThat's rich!
My arm might be unruly sometimes,\nbut at least I don't have a dragon vying\nfor control of my thougths... Ngh!
Tch. Enough talk. It's time to end this.
Aldred, the base is going to collapse!
We should get clear. Though that may\nbe easier said than done...
I'm not doing it to be nice, okay?!\nI just don't think killing you in a cave-in\nwould really prove I'm the strongest.
So I'll let you live, till next we meet.\nAnd then, you—hrgh...\nYou better be ready!
Heh. Yeah, you too.\nI won't hesitate next time.
Nngh...! ...Heh. Heh heh heh...\nHa ha ha ha!
